    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wake up in the future to a world on the brink of extinction. Discover the source of the calamity and save civilization from a mysterious threat. Mine, build, craft and explore a vast interconnected world!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set up a base and explore a vast interconnected world. Regions overlap so you can travel between them with no loading screens required. You can even unlock a rocket to travel to more planets!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic day/night cycle. Different enemies may come out at night and even the seasons change in some regions!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >RPG Leveling System - Level up as you explore, fight mutants and complete quests. Tailor your build by spending skill points and specialize in melee, ranged, energy or minions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 4 Person Multiplayer - Have your friends join to build, explore and fight a variety of epic bosses.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NPC Classes:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Rescue NPCs and add them to your towns. They do more than just sell you things, they craft items automatically and have a daily schedule. Assign them roles such as Blacksmith, Forester, Scientist and much more! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175290/extras/c3e4671cf15c0e9d64a4efa9490f98c9.poster.avif?t=1771791291\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175290/extras/c3e4671cf15c0e9d64a4efa9490f98c9.webm?t=1771791291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175290/extras/c3e4671cf15c0e9d64a4efa9490f98c9.mp4?t=1771791291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build Complex Electrical Systems:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wire up lights, machines and other gadgets. Control lighting and electrical signals through network controls.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175290/extras/86b799fb6d3b3cd95a370c94b97fd936.poster.avif?t=1771791291\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175290/extras/86b799fb6d3b3cd95a370c94b97fd936.webm?t=1771791291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175290/extras/86b799fb6d3b3cd95a370c94b97fd936.mp4?t=1771791291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Automate:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Automate crafting of parts using conveyer belts and tubes to link machines together.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175290/extras/7a71edf2723a46c287812489b4638ec5.poster.avif?t=1771791291\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175290/extras/7a71edf2723a46c287812489b4638ec5.webm?t=1771791291\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175290/extras/7a71edf2723a46c287812489b4638ec5.mp4?t=1771791291\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
